{"tid":506842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【請廣傳】13歲少女陳幃淼失蹤一周 家人報警急尋","createTime":"2017-12-22T15:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-22T15:32:38.000Z","uid":122,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"80eb5c8fa651e630b6634577d2375bea0e80f9cd","tid":506842,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:14:14.000Z","msg":"<strong>【請廣傳】13歲少女陳幃淼失蹤一周 家人報警急尋</strong><br />\n<br />\n即時突發 <br />\n<br />\n2017-12-22 19:15:38 HKT<br />\n<br />\n13歲女童陳幃淼於本月15日晚離開筲箕灣道住所後失蹤，其家人於前日報警，警方今日呼籲市民提供女童的消息。<br />\n<br />\n女童身高約1.54米，體重約68公斤，肥身材，圓面型，黃皮膚，蓄長直黑髮。她最後露面時身穿黑色上衣、黑色運動褲、黑色外套、黑色拖鞋、戴黑框眼鏡及銀色下唇環。<br />\n<br />\n市民如有她的消息或曾見過她，可致電36606490或98860034；或電郵至rmpu-hki@police.gov.hk與港島總區失蹤人口調查組，或與任何一間警署聯絡。"},{"pid":"0b573f3b01501afb9fec8bbd6e2d379576a29f64","tid":506842,"uid":105890,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:15:06.000Z","msg":"1.54m 68kg <br />\n<br />\nconfirmed safe!"},{"pid":"dedfbaf90796077dd4485afa9eca4245bc646f7e","tid":506842,"uid":50801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b573f3b01501afb9fec8bbd6e2d379576a29f64","tid":506842,"uid":105890,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:15:06.000Z","msg":"1.54m 68kg <br />\n<br />\nconfirmed safe!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:16:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674acdf6c52152628bbde7d5b8f9b83d35b0377e","tid":506842,"uid":24083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:16:34.000Z","msg":"13歲就下唇環？"},{"pid":"d4cac47019f433a0baf53f1c4ce3cd56956ceb22","tid":506842,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:17:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1.54m 68kg <br />\n<br />\nconfirmed safe!</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b1036fde094